use your laptop screen as your PI screen view

//Ingredients
A PI that's set up
A Macbook pro 
VNC Viewer from the web - https://www.realvnc.com/en/connect/download/viewer/
Read this https://www.raspberrypi.org/magpi/vnc-raspberry-pi/




// Method
install VNC viewer
follow instructions here https://www.raspberrypi.org/magpi/vnc-raspberry-pi/

